QuestData.Title: I Sunk Your Battleship
QuestData.Description:
Commander, we must expand our fleet if we hope to stand a chance against the Iron Horde.
We have heard reports from Tanaan that a new Horde faction can supply us with the plans to build battleships. Head out there as soon as you can and investigate!
QuestData.PortraitGiverText: Find Shadow Hunter Denjai at Vol'mar in Tanaan Jungle.
QuestData.LogDescription: Meet Shadow Hunter Denjai at Vol'mar in Tanaan Jungle.

Objectives.Objective: Earn Honored Faction with Vol'jin's Headhunters
